name: Android 18 (Dragon Ball) LoRA
description:
Android 18 from the dragon ball series.

This lora was trained not only on anime but also fanart so compared to my other loras it should be more versatile.

Though this also means that this LoRA doesn't produce the natural look of the character from the show that easily so tags like dragon ball, dragon ball z may be required.

Produces very good results with the tags: android 18, blonde hair, blue eyes, short hair

<hypernet:sgqo1n:1.0> is a hypernetwork for the hands that i always have turned on it doesn't affect the final image

Copy the file to stable-diffusion-webui\models\Lora
